This paper focuses on software engineering and specifically on clone detection and refactoring, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to recommend clones for refactoring, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses the extraction of features from software projects, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.SD (Software Development).
